item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Utility_File_Entity
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Utility_File_Entity Datatype Description SoftLayer_Container_Utility_File_Entity data type models a single entity on a storage resource. Entities can include anything within a storage volume including files, folders, directories, and CloudLayer storage projects. Local content A file entity's raw content. Type: binary data contentType A file entity's MIME content type. Type: string createDate The date a file entity was created. Type: dateTime
